<br />

<br />
Why are bards overpowered in the views of most? Simple, Casting on the run > All. And since they are not going to change that any time soon, any nerf will affect other classes more than it will affect bards, cause bards can adapt to the nerf better than any other class. Thus, before you start crying about nerfs, look at the qualities and abilities of your own class, and if you still enjoy playing it, then the more power to you. If you dont, then play a class you enjoy. If none are enjoyable, plz move on to other things and let the rest of us who still find joy in this game to keep on playing the game we like, because after all, it is just that, a game.
<br />

<br />
As someone said, Monks, Rogues or Warriors cant solo anything if their live depended on it. Should we all be nerfed to warriors level of soloability in all fairness? Think not!
